\begin_inset Formula $\tfrac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

 particles, have 
\begin_inset Formula $I=\tfrac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $m=\pm\tfrac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

.
 The energies of these two eigenstates are
\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle \pm\tfrac{1}{2}|\hat{H}_{Z}|\pm\tfrac{1}{2}\right\rangle =\pm\tfrac{1}{2}\omega_{0}$
\end_inset

