\emph default

\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $^{23}$
\end_inset

Na and 
\begin_inset Formula $^{31}$
\end_inset

P).
 All of these are abundant enough in the human body to be imaged directly.
 However, protons are the most common nuclei to image due to their superior
 signal to noise ratio (SNR
